Phase 3 Task 2: Implement tracker.gd (Green Phase)

Replaced placeholder tracker.gd with full implementation (spec Section 6.4).

Implementation:
- extends Node (autoload singleton _GDTCoverage)
- _active: bool — set in _ready() from OS.has_environment("GD_TOOLS_COVERAGE_ACTIVE")
- _hits: Dictionary — keyed by "file_id:line_id", value is hit count
- _ready(): Checks env var, sets _active, prints status if active
- hit(file_id, line_id): No-op if inactive, else increments _hits["file_id:line_id"]
- get_hits(): Returns _hits.duplicate(true) (deep copy)
- reset(): Clears _hits
- is_active(): Returns _active

